Icyorezo cya coronavirus (COVID-19) mu nama y'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'uburayi/umuryango w'ubumwe bw'uburayi n'ubumwe bw'ubwongereza, kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020
Abanduye coronavirus (COVID-19) bagaragaza ubwandu butagira ingano nk'ubw'ibihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'Ubwongereza, kandi rimwe na rimwe, icyorezo cya COVID-19 gikwirakwira mu bihugu byinshi ku isi.
Mu gihe ibi bibaye mu Butaliyani, inzego z'ibanze, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bagomba kongera gahunda zo kwita ku mubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bazakorerwa ubuvuzi bw'umubiri, hamwe n'ubuvuzi bw'ubundi buryo.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, hari ikindi cyorezo cy'indwara y'umutima kitigeze kivugwa cyavutse i Wuhan, mu Ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko icyateye iyi koronavirusi nshya ari icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero ya SARS-CoV-2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Kuva icyo gihe, icyorezo cyatewe na SARS-CoV cyiswe icyorezo cy'indwara y'ibicurane (COVI-19).
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko 80% by'abapfuye bafite uburwayi bukomeye, ni ukuvuga uburwayi butandura bw'ibihaha, kandi ko buri wese apfa.
Mu barwayi 14%, COVID-19 ituma indwara iba ndende cyane bigatuma umuntu aba mu bitaro, mu barwayi 6% iba ikomeye cyane bigatuma abaganga bamwitaho.
Imfu z'abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu bitaro zigera kuri 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, turi kureba uko icyorezo cya COVID-19 gihagaze mu bihugu byose bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EEA n'Ubwongereza (UK) ndetse n'icy'intara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ndashaka kandi kumenya umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 muri iki gihe mu bihugu bya EU/EEA na UK ndetse n'abari mu Butaliyani kuva ku ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA na UK
Nyuma y'Ubushinwa, COVID-19 yageze no mu bindi bihugu, kandi ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu bindi bice by'isi burimo gukurikira.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo ku isi.
Mu kinyamakuru Eurosurveillance cyo ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, Spiteri al. yatangaje ko ari ubwa mbere mu Burayi habonetse abarwayi ba COVID-19 nk'uko bitangazwa na WHO.
Mu muryango w'ibihugu by'ubumwe bw'Uburayi na EAC, ku wa 24 Mutarama 2020 nibwo hatangajwe ubwa mbere ko mu Bufaransa habonetse abarwayi batatu mu baturage bo mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, abantu banduye COVID-19 bari mu bihugu 30 bigize EU/EEA ndetse n'Ubwongereza, aho ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 kugeza ubu hari hamaze kuboneka abantu 39,768 banduye, 1,727 bapfuye, n'abantu 1,441 bapfuye mu bindi bihugu bitandukanye uretse u Butaliyani.
Gukurikirana imibare y'abanduye COVID-19
Ikigo cy'u Burayi Gishinzwe Kurwanya no Gutegeka Indwara (ECDC), gitanga imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu byose byo ku isi, bigizwe n'abantu bafite ubushobozi nk'abayobozi b'inzego z'ubuzima, abayobozi b'ibihugu n'ab'imijyi hamwe na WHO, bagenzurwa buri munsi saa munani z'amanywa.
Aya makuru ni yo akoreshwa cyane mu gupima COVID-19 muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, ndetse no mu Butaliyani.
Nk'igishushanyo cy'umubare w'abarwaye COVID-19, tubarura umubare w'abafite ubwandu bwa COVID-19, mu gihe tubarura ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu bihugu byose bigize EU/EEA na UK kuva ku itariki ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Twerekanye kandi imibare rusange y'abanduye muri buri gihugu ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani z'amanywa, aho twavuga ko mu Butaliyani hari hagati ya tariki ya 31 Mutarama na 15 Werurwe 2020.
Imibare ya COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA na UK.
Imibare y'ibanze y'abanduye COVID-19 mu minsi 14 ishize mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza ikurikira cyane cyane iy'intara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Ifoto ya 1).
Mu bihugu byose bigize EU/EEA na UK, imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 yatangiye kugabanuka ku ya 21 Gashyantare, ikomeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (Ibindi).
Ibi ahanini byatewe n'umubare muke w'abanduye muri Italy, ariko n'ibindi bihugu byose bya EU/EEA ndetse n'Ubwongereza byerekana ko hari ihinduka mu mubare w'abanduye COVID-19 (Ibindi).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza imibare y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19, mu bihugu bya EU/EEA na UK mu gihe cy'amezi atandatu n'igice mu gihe cy'Ubutaliyani kuva ku ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Byemezwa ko, ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa munani z'amanywa, ibihugu 15 bya EU/EEA n'ibindi bihugu byo mu Bwongereza byatangaje umubare w'abanduye ushobora kugereranywa n'u Butaliyani mu minsi 3 mbere cyangwa nyuma y'uko igihe kirangira.
Ibi byerekana ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 batangajwe ushobora kuba muke cyane ugereranyije n'abatuye EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza.
Ubushakashatsi dukora ku cyorezo cya COVID-19 bugaragaza ko iki cyorezo gifite ingaruka zishobora kuvugwa mu bihugu byose.
Ibi biterwa n'ibihugu by'amahanga, impinduka mu byemezo by'ubuvuzi, n'ibimenyetso by'ubwandu mu bihugu bitandukanye hamwe n'uburyo bwo guhitamo abarwayi bagomba kongera gusuzumwa kubera COVID-19, hamwe n'ubushakashatsi.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga mu turere tw'u Butaliyani twanduye bagaragaje ko 10% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi bw'ibanze kandi amakuru avuga ko ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bo muri utwo turere bitagishoboye kubikora.
Raporo y'abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu bitaro na/cyangwa mu bigo byita ku barwayi iri ku kigero cya 6% na 1% mu bihugu bya EU/EEA (ibipimo birahari).
Nyuma, ibyo byose byashyizwe hamwe mu gice kimwe kugira ngo hatangwe amakuru y'ubugenzuzi agaragaza imibare y'abanduye n'abapfuye.
Ubundi bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2010-2011 bwagaragaje impinduka mu mibare y'ibitanda n'amabwiriza y'ubuvuzi mu burayi, kuva ku bitanda 29.2 mu Budage kugeza kuri 4.2 ku bantu 100,000 muri Portugal.
Ibihugu byerekana ko bishobora kugira ubukene buri hasi cyangwa hejuru ugereranyije n'Ubutaliyani (ibitanda 12.5 by'ubuvuzi n'ubuvuzi bwa nyuma ku baturage 100,000 mu 2010-11).
Gutegura gahunda zigena uburyo bwo kwakira, hamwe n'ibisabwa na buri gihugu cya EU/EEA na UK byo kwakira abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwivuza no gukenera ibitanda bakeneye bagomba kuba bafite amabwiriza yo kwivuza ku giti cyabo nibura 90% by'ibanze by'ibaruwa y'ubugenzuzi ya ECDC ku bipimo bya COVID-19.
Kubera ko umubare w'abanduye wiyongereye mu bice bimwe na bimwe by'ibihugu bya EU/EEA na UK, kandi ibitaro n'amatsinda y'abashinzwe kwita ku barwayi bakorera mu byumba byakira abarwayi, amakuru y'abarwayi n'ibitanda byateganijwe ashobora kuboneka mu bice byose by'umujyi wa Mardi Gras kubera ikibazo cya 2 cy'uburwayi (NUTS-2).
Ibyabaye mu Butaliyani n'ibibera mu bindi bihugu bigaragaza ko COVID-19 ikomeje kwiyongera mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bigomba gutegura uburyo bwo gufasha abaturage guhangana na SARS-CoV-2 hamwe no kwiyongera kw'umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi, hamwe n'ubundi buvuzi, nk'uko bigenda mu turere tw'Ubutaliyani twugarijwe n'icyorezo.
Nkuko byerekanwe mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe na ECDC, nta buryo buhagije bwo kwirinda ikwirakwira rya SARS-COV-2, kandi uburyo bwo guhera ku kwivuza bukagenda bugabanuka, kuko umubare w'abarwayi ukomeza kwiyongera ntabwo uha umwanya uhagije abashinzwe kurwanya indwara gusobanukirwa, guhangana no kurwanya uburyo bwo guhangana n'ibiza mu gihe gikwiriye.
Ibizamini by'ubwandu bw'ibicurane byongeraho ingamba za leta zo kugabanya ubukana bw'iki cyorezo.
Hari icyizere cy'uko ibihugu bishobora guhangana n'ikibazo cy'ubwandu bw'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga.
Niba ibi bitaraba, birashoboka ko gahunda y'ubuvuzi mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe bya EU/EEA izaba ifite ibibazo bitewe n'umubare w'abarwayi bakeneye ubuvuzi mu bindi bihugu uzagenda wiyongera mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), kizwiho kuba giterwa n'indwara y'ibicurane by'ibicurane (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 3,000 no kwandura abarenga 80,000 mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bihugu byo ku isi, bikaba ari ikibazo cy'abantu benshi.
Nk'uko bigaragara, SARS-CoV, yateje SARS mu bantu babarirwa mu bihumbi mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwandura binyuze mu nyoni kandi igatanga ibimenyetso by'indwara nk'uko bigenda ku bantu.
By'umwihariko, COVID-19 ifite ubwandu buciriritse cyane ugereranyije na SARS cyangwa se ikandura cyane kandi yibasira cyane abantu bakuze kurusha abitaho n'abagabo kurusha abagore.
