Umunsi mukuru w'impeshyi wabaye ku ya 25 Mutarama 2020 wabaye umunsi utazibagirana ku baturage bose bo mu Bushinwa bari mu bihe byo kuguma mu rugo mu gihe cy'ikiruhuko cya buri cyumweru kubera icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Iyi virusi imeze nka koronavirusi (CoV) yateje icyorezo cy'indwara y'umutima y'ibicurane (SARS) mu 2003; bityo Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryitiriye iyi ndwara SARS-CoV-2, kandi iyi ndwara yitwa Icyorezo cya COVID-19 (COVID-19).
Iki cyorezo cyatangiriye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, nyuma kiza gukwirakwira mu gihugu cyose ndetse no mu bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi.
Kuva ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, virusi imaze kwandura abantu 80.000 bagaragaweho COVID-19, aho abagera ku 40.000 bakize n'abagera ku 3.000 bapfuye.
OMS iravuga ko COVID-19 ari "icyorezo cyugarije abantu" kandi ko gishobora guteza akaga gakomeye.
Nk'uko byatangajwe na PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed), mbere y'uko habaho ibyumweru bibiri, inyandiko zirenga 200 zatanzwe ku COVID-19 hamwe n'ubumenyi ku ndwara, urukingo, gusuzuma no kuvura kuva ku itariki ya 7 Mutarama 2020 aho inyandiko ya mbere yagaragaje ko iyo ndwara itandukanye mu barwayi benshi.
Iki cyemezo cyatumye habaho ubushakashatsi bushya mu by'ubumenyi bushya kandi bwihuse.
Urugero, tugiye kurebera hamwe icyorezo cya COVID-19 na SARS hamwe n'icyorezo cy'indwara y'ibicurane byo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS, icyorezo cya 2012).
