Polyproteins zishobora gukoreshwa mu gukora poroteyine zitagira ingirabuzima fatizo 16, zitwa nsp1~16.
Ibindi bice by'urusobe rwa genom bigizwe na ORF zigenewe gutangiza poroteyine, harimo umutwe (S), uruhu (E), uruhu (M) na nucleoprotein (N).
Hariho ubwoko bw'indwara zitandukanye ziterwa n'ubwoko butandukanye bwa CoV.
Bitewe n'ubwoko bw'ibanze bwa poroteyine, CoVs zishobora kugabanywamo amatsinda ane (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV na delta-CoV), aho beta-CoVs ari zo ziganjemo CoVs kandi zigizwe n'itsinda ry'ibanze ry'ibanze (A, B, C na D).
