Amategeko y'icyorezo: (1) amateka y'ingendo cyangwa gutura mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu turere tuwukikije, hamwe n'abaturage aho abantu banduye COVID-19 batangajwe mu minsi 14 ishize mbere y'ihindagurika ry'ibimenyetso; (2) amateka y'abanduye SARS-CoV-2 (binyuze mu gupima acide nucleic ku ruhu); (3) amateka y'abarwayi bagaragaza uburwayi cyangwa ibimenyetso byo guhumeka mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu turere tuwukikije, cyangwa abaturage COVID-19 batangajwe mu minsi 14 ishize mbere y'ihindagurika ry'ibimenyetso; (4) amateka y'abantu banduye icyorezo (2 cyangwa barenga batangajwe mu byumweru bibiri by'uburwayi no/cyangwa ibimenyetso byo guhumeka mu biraro, mu ngo, mu mirimo, mu bitaro, mu bindi bigo by'ubuvuzi).
Ibimenyetso: (1) guhinda umushyitsi/kudahumeka neza; (2) ibimenyetso bya COVID-19; (3) umubare w'amaraso y'umuntu ugabanutse, cyangwa umubare w'indwara ya Lymphocyte wagabanutse mu ntangiriro.
Gusuzuma inyamaswa z'ibibembe bizwi ko zanduye bigomba kuba byuzuye kandi bifite ibimenyetso cyangwa ibimenyetso by'umubiri nk'ibi: (1) PCR igaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 ifite virusi; (2) ibice bya genome yose ya virusi bigaragaza ko ifitanye isano ya hafi na koronavirusi nshya zizwi; (3) ifite IgM ifite ubushobozi bwo kurwanya IgG ifite ubushobozi bwo kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 mu gusuzuma amaraso; cyangwa ihinduka ry'umubiri igG ifite ubushobozi bwo kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 ntihaba iriho, cyangwa se iriyongera inshuro 4 cyangwa zirenga mu gihe cy'ifunguro ry'umunsi cyangwa mu gihe cy'imibonano mpuzabitsina.
