Abanyeshuri b'Abashinwa bo muri kaminuza zo muri Amerika batangiye ibikorwa byo gutanga imfashanyo mu bice by'u Bushinwa byibasiwe n'icyorezo, hamwe n'imiryango yo mu Karere ka Chicago yahagaritse ibikorwa byo gutanga udupfukamunwa tw'ubwoko bwa N95 50.000 ku bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei ku ya 30 Mutarama.Umuryango w'ubutabazi Direct Relief, ufatanyije na FedEx, wohereje udupfukamunwa tw'ubwoko 200,000 n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubwirinzi, birimo udupfukamunwa n'udupfukamunwa, mu bikorwa by'ubutabazi byabereye i Wuhan Union Hospital ku ya 30 Mutarama.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje inkunga ya miliyoni 100 z'amadolari ya Amerika kuri OMS yo gukora ubushakashatsi ku rukingo n'imiti no kurwanya "abaturage bo muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'Epfo bashobora kwandura".
Interaksiyo yatangaje ko leta y'Ubushinwa yohereje udupfukamunwa ku bantu 200,000 bo muri Filipine ku ya 6 Gashyantare, nyuma y'aho Senateri Richard Gordon yohereje udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16 i Wuhan.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, Croix Rouge ya Singapour yatangaje ko izohereza inkunga ya miliyoni 2.26 z'amadolari y'Amerika mu Bushinwa.
Ubuyapani bwatanze udupfukamunwa tw'ubwoko butandukanye i Wuhan, Turukiya yatanze amabwiriza y'ubuvuzi, Uburusiya bwohereje toni 13 z'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi i Wuhan, Malaysia yatangaje ko yatanze toni 18 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa, Ubudage bwohereje toni 10 000 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'ibikoresho by'ubushakashatsi bya Hazmat, Amerika yohereje toni 17.8 z'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa kandi itanga inkunga y'amadolari y'Amerika asaga miliyoni 100 mu bufasha n'amafaranga mu bihugu byibasiwe n'icyorezo.
Muri Werurwe, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'Uburusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'abaganga mu Butaliyani mu kurwanya icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Umuhanzi Jack Ma yohereje kopi miliyoni 1.1 z'ibizamini, miliyoni 6 z'udupfukamunwa, n'udupfukamunwa 60,000 mu mujyi wa Addis Ababa muri Ethiopia kugira ngo tuhabwe Umuryango w'Afurika Yunze Ubumwe.
Nyuma yaho yohereje ibikoresho byo gupima 5,000, udupfukamunwa 100,000 na za orudinateri eshanu muri Panama.
Yatanze kandi Canada ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi. Ubuholandi, Espagne, Turukiya, Georgia na Repubulika ya Tchèque byatangaje ko bihangayikishijwe n'ibicuruzwa by'imashini z'ubushakashatsi zikorerwa mu Bushinwa.
