Icyorezo cya coronavirus cyateje ibibazo byinshi birimo ibiza, kubera ko ibigo by'ubuvuzi bikora cyane mu guhangana n'icyorezo ku isi hose, ubwoba bwo kugura, guhagarika inganda no gutembera.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ibiyobyabwenge n'imiti cyatangaje ko hari ibibazo by'ubuvuzi n'ubuvuzi bitewe n'uko ibipimo by'ibiyobyabwenge biri hejuru kandi n'ababikora baragabanutse.
Ibihugu byinshi kandi byatewe n'ubwoba bwo kugura ibintu by'ibanze, nk'ibiribwa, ibikoresho byo mu nzu, amazi meza, bituma bidakomeza gutangwa.
Uburyo bwikoranabuhanga ahanini bushingiye ku kwihutisha gutwara ibintu nk'amabwiriza.
Nk'uko byatangajwe na Tedros Adhanom, umuyobozi wa mbere wa OMS, igitekerezo cyo kwambara udupfukamunwa cyarushijeho kwiyongera ku kigero cya 100.
