Ibicuruzwa by'ibikoresho byo kwambara ku isi biragoye kuboneka, kandi WHO ifite impungenge ko bishobora guteza ibibazo by'ubuzima ku bikoresha.
Muri Australia, icyorezo cyatumye abaguzi benshi ba Australia bagura ibicuruzwa byabo mu Bushinwa.
Iki gikorwa cyatumye ibikoresho by'abana b'impinja biboneka mu maduka y'ibanze ndetse na leta ya Australia irabihagarika.Nubwo umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani no mu karere ka Wuhan, hamwe n'ibihano ku biribwa byinshi, uturere twombi ntabwo dufite ibibazo by'ibiribwa.
Uburyo Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani bwashyizeho bwo gucuruza no kugurisha ibicuruzwa mu buryo buhoraho, bufite ingaruka ku kugabanuka kw'ibura ry'ibiribwa mu Burayi no muri Amerika ya Ruguru.
