Ijambo "gukaraba intoki" mu yandi magambo, risobanura ko wemera ko uba uri mu bikorwa cyangwa mu bikorwa by'ubutabazi.
Intangiriro y'inkuru ya Matayo ivuga ko Ponsiyo Pilato yafashwe mu gihe cyo kugerageza kwica Yesu Kristo, ariko ni inkuru ifite ibisobanuro byinshi mu bantu bo mu Bwongereza.
Muri Macbeth ya Shakespeare, Lady Macbeth atangira akaraba intoki kubera ko yifuzaga kwihana ibyaha bimwe na bimwe yari afite, byerekana ko yari afite icyaha cyo kwica umugabo we.
Basanze kandi abaturage, nyuma yo gukaraba cyangwa gutekereza ku bintu byahise, bakaraba intoki kenshi kurusha abandi bantu, kandi bakemera ko gukaraba intoki ari ngombwa.
Ikindi kandi, abantu bafite akamenyero ko gukaraba intoki nyuma y'ibi bikorwa bashobora gukora imirimo yo "kwisukura" nk'ubufasha.
Abahanga mu bya dini batanga inama yo gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'isuku no kwirinda.Icyigisho cyo gukaraba intoki, n'amazi adafite isabune, gisa n'ikijya mu bikorwa by'abandi bahanga benshi, harimo Aba-Bahá'í, Abahindu, Tevilah na Netilat Yadayim mu idini rya Kiyahudi, Lavabo mu idini rya Masinji, na Wudhu mu idini rya Isilamu.Aba-Dina na bo batanga inama yo gukaraba intoki, cyane cyane nyuma y'ibikorwa.
Abahindu, Abayahudi n'Abislamu bakunze gukaraba intoki mbere yo kuva mu rugo.
Mu idini ry'abahindu, ababuda, aba sikism, aba judaïsme n'aba islam, abantu bose basabwa gukaraba intoki mbere na nyuma yo kurya.
Ingamba zo kwirinda impanuka zo mu kazi kubera COVID-19
Gucunga ibyago byo mu kazi kubera COVID-19 ni uburyo bwo gukoresha ibigo by'ubuvuzi mu kwirinda icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Ibipimo by'ibyago byo mu kazi bigenda bihinduka bitewe n'aho umuntu akorera n'ubwoko bw'akazi akora, bitewe n'ibipimo by'ibyago byo kuboneka, ubwandu bw'indwara mu baturage, hamwe n'ibintu bishobora gutuma abakozi bahura n'ibyago byo kwandura COVID-19.
Ikigo cy'ubwiteganyirize cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe umutekano n'ubuzima (OSHA) kivuga ko imirimo yoroheje idafite ibyago byinshi byo guhura n'abaturage cyangwa abandi bakozi, aho ingamba zo kwirinda indwara zisabwa, nko gukaraba intoki, guhagarika abakozi bake mu rugo igihe barwaye, kugenzura umwuka, no gusukura no gusukura ibikoresho by'akazi.
Imirimo y'ibanze iteje akaga ni iy'abakora ingendo zitemewe cyangwa z'abanduye COVID-19, ariko bashobora kwandura bitewe n'ubwandu bw'abantu cyangwa ingendo z'amahanga.
Ibi birimo abakozi bafite ubushobozi bwo guhura n'abantu benshi nko mu mashuri, ahantu hakorerwa imirimo hari abantu benshi, ahantu hari ibicuruzwa byinshi.
Ingamba zo kwirinda iki cyorezo, usibye ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda, zirimo kwirinda indwara ziterwa n'ibicurane, kwambara udupfukamunwa, no kwambara imyenda y'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri mu gihe uhuye n'umuntu ufite COVID-19.
OSHA ivuga ko abaganga n'abakora mu by'ubuvuzi bapfa kubera ko bagaragaye ubwabo cyangwa hari undi muntu ushobora kuba afite COVID-19 ari mu bafite ibyago by'indwara, ibyo bikaba byongera ibyago byo kwandura iyo abakozi bakoze ibikorwa byo kohereza umwuka, gutunganya, cyangwa kuvura imiti, ku muntu ufite cyangwa ushobora kuba afite COVID-19.
Ibipimo by'ibyago bikenewe kuri aba bakozi birimo ibipimo by'ibikoresho by'ubwubatsi nk'ibyuma by'umwuka, hamwe n'ibikoresho by'ubwikorezi bijyanye n'akazi.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora guteza ibibazo byinshi mu kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kudahita bajya ku kazi kubera uburwayi, kubera ko baba bakeneye kwita ku bandi, cyangwa kubera ko batinya ko bashobora kurwara.
Ibisobanuro byubucuruzi birashobora guhinduka, byombi biterwa nibikoresho byibanda kubyo batwara, hamwe nuburyo bwo kubona ibicuruzwa (urugero, kugura mugihe ibicuruzwa bibuze, cyangwa kubakozi bo mu rugo cyangwa kubitwara mu modoka).
Mu gusoza, kohereza ibikoresho mu duce twatewe na COVID-19 bishobora guhagarikwa. Gutegura gahunda cyangwa igisubizo cy'icyorezo bishobora kuba ingenzi mu kurinda ibikorwa.
Gahunda zigabanya ibyago byose bijyanye n'aho ukorera n'ibikorwa nk'ibyo, nk'ubwibone, ibintu bishobora guteza akaga mu rugo no mu baturage, hamwe n'ibintu bishobora guteza akaga ku bantu bakorana nk'ubushomeri cyangwa indwara.
Byatangiye kandi gushyiraho ingamba zo kugabanya ibyago nk'ibyo, hamwe n'ingamba zo kwirinda ibintu bishobora guteza ibibazo nk'ibimenyetso by'indwara.
Gutegura no gusubiza gahunda z'icyorezo bishobora kuba mu nzego z'igihugu cyangwa intara.
Uburyo bwo guhangana n'iki cyorezo burimo kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara ku bakozi, abashinzwe kwita ku bantu bafite ibyago byo kurwara izindi ndwara, gukomeza ubucuruzi, no kugabanya ibyago by'indwara mu bindi bice by'ingendo.
Ibibazo by'icyorezo mu baturage aho ubucuruzi bubera bigira ingaruka ku buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga.
Ingamba zo kwirinda ibyago ni uburyo bukoreshwa mu nzego z'ubuzima n'ubuvuzi mu gushyiraho ingamba hamwe n'itsinda ry'abantu kandi z'ingirakamaro.
Mu gihe nta buryo bushoboka bwo kwirinda ibyago bya COVID-19, ingamba z'ibanze ni ugusuzuma abashinzwe ubwubatsi, hakurikiyeho kugenzura ibikorwa, hanyuma amaherezo n'ibikoresho byo kwipfuka.
Ingufu z'ubwubatsi zirimo imyitwarire y'abakozi hamwe n'ibyago by'akazi bidashingiye ku myitwarire y'abakozi, kandi bishobora kuba uburyo bwiza cyane.
