Ibikoresho byose bya PPE bigomba guhitamo kubijyanye n'ibyago bigera ku mukoresha, bigomba gufatwa nk'ibikenewe (urugero nk'ibikoresho byo guhumeka), bikagaragara neza kandi bikagaragara, bigasuzumwa, bikagororwa, bigasimbuzwa igihe bibaye ngombwa, bikagaragara neza, bikagaragara, bigatwarwa cyangwa bigashyirwa hanze kubera ubwandu.
