Katherine, CRT (Amanda K, Amy V, Bryan J, Doreen D, Gregory V, James V, Joel L, Lynette L, Ryan M, na Tony S), hamwe n'abandi bagize Inteko Ishinga Amategeko (Grant I, Heather W, James V, Janeen U, Lisa S, Robyn A, Ryan M, na Toby N).
bAngiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) ni ikinyabutabire gifasha mu kuvura indwara mu bice by'umubiri (imbere mu ngirabuzimafatizo) by'ibihaha, mu maraso, mu mutima, mu nda no mu byondo.
ACE2 ihagarika ibikorwa by'umusemburo wa angiotensin-II (ACE) binyuze mu kugabanya umuvuduko wa angiotensin-II no kongera ingano ya Angiotensin (α) 1-7) bigatuma ishobora kuba umuti mwiza mu kuvura indwara z'umutima. ACE2 ikora nk'urugi mu ngirabuzimafatizo zimwe na zimwe za koronavirusi.
Ubwoko bw'amavuta umuntu aterwa n'ibinyampeke ni bwo bwitwa ACE2.
Igikoresho cya Angiotensin 2 ni metaloenzyme ikubiyemo zinc kandi iherereye ku gice cy'inyuma cy'umubiri n'ibindi bice by'umubiri.
Poroteyine ya ACE2 ifite N-terminal peptidase M2 domain na C-terminal collectrin ya jenoside ya amino acids transporter domain.
ACE2 ni imwe mu poroteyine z'uruhu rw'umubiri wa mbere, ifite ingufu nyinshi kandi ikora ku ngirabuzimafatizo zo mu maraso no mu bindi bice by'umubiri.
Uru rugingo rwa ACE2 ruri hanze y'ingirabuzimafatizo ruba rufitanye isano n'uru rugingo rwa transmembrane binyuze mu buryo bw'imikorere ya sheddase, maze poroteyine zigize uru rugingo zigatangira kwinjira mu maraso, amaherezo zikava mu mubiri.
ACE2 iboneka mu bice byinshi by'umubiri: ACE2 ifatanye n'urusobe rw'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ibihaha, ingirabuzimafatizo z'ubwonko z'ubwoko bwa II, uturemangingo duto cyane tw'amaraso, ingirabuzimafatizo z'amaraso n'iz'amaraso n'ingirabuzimafatizo z'umusatsi mu bice byinshi by'umubiri.
Urubuga rwa ACE2 mRNA rwasanzwe kandi mu gice cy'ubwonko cyitwa cerebral cortex, striatum, hypothalamus, n'ibinure by'ubwonko.
Uruhare rw'ibanze rwa ACE2 ni nk'urw'igiciro cyo kurwanya ACE.
ACE ihindura ingirabuzima fatizo ya angiotensin I ikora nk'isosiyete y'imikorere y'amaraso (angiotensin II).
ACE2 nayo ihindura amino acide phenylalanine ifite karboxyl-terminal mu angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) ikora ku byuma byongera amaraso (angiotensin 1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 ishobora no kuvamo ibindi bice byinshi bya peptides nka [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, na ghrelin.
ACE2 nayo ikumira umusemburo wa amino acide SLC6A19 kandi ishobora kuba intandaro y'indwara ya Hartnup.
Nk'indwara y'uruhu, ACE2 ikora nk'urugi rw'ingirabuzimafatizo mu zindi koronavirusi, zirimo HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virusi itera SARS); na SARS-CoV-2 (virusi yatumye COVID-19 ibaho).
Ikindi kandi, guhuza poroteyine ya S1 ya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 mu gice cy'umusemburo ACE2 ku ngirabuzimafatizo bigira uruhare mu gutuma virusi ebyiri z'iyo virusi zidakora neza kandi zigakora neza ku ndwara z'indwara z'ibice by'imbere mu ngirabuzimafatizo.
Iyi ndwara ituma habaho uburyo bwo kuvura poroteyine ya S binyuze mu cyuma cyitwa TMPRSS2 cyakira serine protease, indwara ikaba irimo gukorwaho ubushakashatsi nk'umuti. Ibi byatumye dutekereza ko kugabanya ibipimo bya ACE2, mu ngirabuzimafatizo, bishobora kugira akamaro mu kuvura iyi ndwara.
Ariko, imiryango myinshi y'abahanga n'inzego zishinzwe amategeko zasabye gukomeza gukoresha ACE inhibitor n'imiti ya ARB.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bushakashatsi bwose bwakozwe ku itariki ya 11 Nyakanga 2012, bwagaragaje ko "gukoresha ACE inhibitors byahitanye ibyago bya 34% byo kurwara pneumonia ugereranyije n'ibindi".
Byongeye kandi, "ibyago byo kurwara ibicurane byagabanutse mu barwayi bavurwa ACE inhibitors bafite ibyago byo kurwara ibicurane, cyane cyane mu barwayi bafite umuvuduko w'amaraso n'umutima.
Kufata ACE inhibitors nabyo byahitanye abantu benshi cyane ku ndwara ya Pneumonia, nubwo ibimenyetso byagabanutse ku byago byose bya Pneumonia".
Umuntu uvukana ACE2 (rhACE2) ni umuti mushya mu kuvura ibicurane by'ibicurane, kandi ushobora kongera umuvuduko w'amaraso mu bicurane no guhumeka mu bana b'impanga barwaye indwara y'ibicurane by'ibicurane by'ibicurane.
Igihe cy'ikirenga cy'ubuzima bwa rhACE2 mu bantu ni amasaha 10 kandi igikorwa cya mbere ni iminota 30 ndetse n'igihe cy'ikirenga cy'umuvuduko (igihe) ni amasaha 24.
Hari ibimenyetso byinshi bigaragaza ko rhACE2 ishobora kuba umuti mwiza ku bantu batemera imiti isanzwe ya angiotensin system (RAS inhibitors) cyangwa ku ndwara ziterwa na angiotensin II. RhACE2 yavuye mu mazi yageragejwe mu bizamini byo kuvura indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero.
Porogaramu za COVID-19 ni porogaramu zashyizweho mu rwego rwo gufasha abantu kumenya amakuru mu buryo bworoshye mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus cya 2019-20, nko kumenya abantu ("abafatanyabikorwa") bashobora kuba bari kumwe n'umuntu wanduye.
Hariho uburyo bwinshi bwo gukora cyangwa bwemewe, hamwe na leta n'ubufasha bwigenga mu turere n'intara.
Ibisobanuro byuburyo bwo kwerekana porogaramu z'ububiko byatanzwe.
Ibibazo by'ubudahemuka byaravutse, cyane cyane ku buryo bwo kumenya aho abantu bakoresha ibyo bikoresho baba.
Uburyo bwo kumenya amakuru y'umuntu bukoresha ibimenyetso bya Bluetooth mu kumenya aho umuntu ari cyangwa aho ari.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byatangaje icyarimwe ko bagiye gushyiraho uburyo bwo gushyigikira porogaramu za Bluetooth muri sisitemu y'imikorere ya Android na iOS.
Mu Bushinwa, leta y'Ubushinwa, ifatanyije na Alipay, yashyizeho porogaramu zitandukanye zituma abaturage bamenya niba bari kumwe n'abantu banduye COVID-19.
Abantu bakoresha ubu buryo mu mijyi 200 yo mu Bushinwa.
Ikoranabuhanga ryakozwe n'abakozi ba IT, ryatangajwe nk'irisanzwe kandi ryugururiwe abantu bose, kandi ryatangarijwe inzego za leta. Muri Macédoine y'Amajyaruguru hari porogaramu ikorana na Bluetoth yitwa "StopKorona!", igamije kugaragaza ibyago byo guhura n'abarwayi no guha igisubizo kiza inzego z'ubuzima.
Porogaramu yaturutse mu bikorwa by'ibigo by'ikoranabuhanga n'ubuzima.
Ku ya 14 Mata 2020, porogaramu yari imaze kwemererwa kwinjira mu bubiko bwa Google Play na Apple App Store.
Ku ya 12 Mata, leta yatangaje ko porogaramu yo guhashya icyorezo izaba ibonetse mu byumweru bike.Ibipimo by'ubu buryo byararangiye muri Irilande, n'u Bufaransa ("StopCovid").
Australia na New Zealand barimo gusuzuma uburyo bwo gukoresha ikoranabuhanga rishingiye ku ikoranabuhanga rya TraceTogether Singapore hamwe n'ikoranabuhanga rya BlueTrace.Uburusiya bwiteze gushyiraho uburyo bwo gukoresha ikoranabuhanga mu gupima abarwayi ba COVID-19 bari i Moscow, kugira ngo bumve kandi bumve ko batagomba kuva mu ngo zabo.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu mu by'ubushakashatsi mu by'umutekano muri Kaminuza ya Cambridge, yavuze ko ibibazo by'imikorere by'ibikoresho bishobora kubaho, nko kugaragaza umuntu nk'uwari ufite ikibazo ariko atari byo, bishobora kuba ingenzi cyane mu gihe ari mu bantu bake.
Mu kwirinda impungenge z'uko porogaramu z'ikoranabuhanga zishobora kuba ari impimbano cyangwa z'amayeri, Apple yagaragaje ko hari inzitizi ku buryo ibigo bishobora kongera porogaramu zifitanye isano na coronavirus mu bubiko bwayo bwa App Store, bikazibuza "kujya" ku bigo cyangwa ku bigo byemewe.
Google na Amazon byasimbuye ibyo bigo.
Abantu bafite impungenge z'umutekano muke bagaragaje impungenge ku bijyanye n'uko abantu bose bakwirinda coronavirus, cyane cyane niba gahunda yo kwirinda coronavirus yatangajwe izahagarikwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo.
Amnesty International n'andi mashyirahamwe arenga 100 y'abaharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu, batangaje ko hari ibindi birego byinshi by'uko abantu bakomeje gufatwa muri ubwo buryo.
Aya matsinda yatangaje ko afite impungenge ku mikorere ya leta:
Gucunga bishobora kuba "byiza, ingirakamaro cyangwa bibi";
gushyiraho amategeko agenga imanza no kugenzura ko amategeko agenga imanza akurikizwa;
ibikorwa n'amakuru bibujijwe mu buryo bw'ibanze ku bijyanye na COVID-19.
umutekano w'amakuru n'ibimenyetso bitagaragara bigomba kubikwa neza kandi bigomba kuba bihuje n'ibisubizo;
gucunga amakuru bigomba kuba ari uburyo bwo kubara no kugenzura ibicuruzwa;
gusangira amakuru n'undi muntu wese bigomba gukurikizwa;
uburyo bwo guhangana n'ibibazo bizaterwa n'uko abaturage bahanganye n'ibibazo;
Kwita ku bantu bose muri ubu buryo binyuze mu "bikorwa by'ingenzi" bigomba guhuzwa, nk'uko bikorwa n'abakozi b'ubuzima n'imiryango yemewe. Ikigo cy'ikoranabuhanga cya German Chaos Computer Club (CCC) na Reporters Without Borders (Reporter ohne Grenzen) (RSF) na byo byatanze inama.
Porogaramu ya Google/Apple ishaka gukemura ikibazo cy'ubugenzuzi bukurikiraho mu gukuraho uburyo bwo kwerekana aho umuntu ari mu makuru yabo nyuma y'igihe runaka.
Ibihugu bimwe na bimwe bikoresha uburyo bwo kugenzura ariko ntibikoreshe porogaramu, bigakora nta kurengaho porogaramu cyangwa uburyo nta wundi muntu uzakurikira.
Muri Isirayeli, gahunda yo kwita ku bantu no kubashyira mu kato yari yemewe.
Uburyo bwo kugenzura aho umuntu ari bushobora kugira ingaruka ku makuru yiringirwa y'abantu.
Ariko, ntabwo sisitemu zose n'ibigo by'ububanyi n'amahanga bikeneye kwinjira mu makuru y'ibanga; hari uburyo bwo kubika amakuru yatanzwe bujya butangwa na serivisi z'ububanyi n'amahanga kugirango bihindure amakuru (kubikora mu matsinda yo hasi).
Muri Koreya y'Epfo, hari uburyo butari ku byangombwa bufasha mu kurwanya ubusambanyi.
Hakoreshejwe porogaramu itanga, sisitemu ikora amakuru y'ibanze y'ibanze muburyo butandukanye nko kumenyesha amakuru ya terefone na karita ya banki, kandi ikoresha byose kugirango itange ubutumwa bwanditse kubantu bashobora kurwara.
Uretse gukoresha amakuru y'ibanze, leta yashyizeho amakuru y'ibanze ku baturage, bitewe n'impinduka mu mabwiriza y'amakuru nyuma y'icyorezo cya MERS muri iki gihugu.
Aya makuru aba ari rusange ku bantu benshi binyuze mu bikorwa byinshi n'ibikoresho.Ibihugu nk'u Budage birimo kugerageza guhuza uburyo bwo kubika amakuru n'ibikoresho by'ibanze.
Tariki ya 6 Mata 2020, amakuru azasohoka uko yakabaye.
Gukurikirana aho amakuru abitswe ari birazwi, hamwe n'imyitozo y'abashakashatsi kubijyanye na mudasobwa.Ku ya 7 Mata 2020, abahanga barenga icumi bakoresheje uburyo bwo kubika amakuru, nko gukoresha Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) kugirango bakoreshe abakoresha telefone zitandukanye.
Nyamara, PEPP-PT ni uburyo buhuriweho bufite uburyo bw'itumanaho n'ubw'itumanaho, kandi ntabwo ari bumwe. Uburyo bw'itumanaho burimo Decentralized Privacy-Preserving Proximity Tracing (DP-PPT/DP-3T), Temporary Contact Numbers (TCN, cyangwa Contact Event Numbers, CEN), Privacy Sensitive Protocols and Mechanisms for Mobile Contact Tracing (PACT) n'ibindi.
Muri ubwo buryo, amakuru ashobora kuboneka ntabwo aba ari mu buryo, kandi buri muyoboro utangwa mu buryo butandukanye.
Itsinda ry'ibanga rya MIT Media Lab ryatangije uburyo bwo gukoresha SafePaths, uburyo bwo gukoresha uburyo bwo kubika amakuru mu gihe cyo gukusanya amakuru no gukoresha amakuru y'aho umuntu ari n'aho ari kugira ngo barinde ikwirakwira rya COVID-19.
Byashingiye ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu gitabo cyitwa "Apps Gone Rogue: Maintaining Personal Privacy in an Epidemic" cyasohotse muri Werurwe 2020.
SafeTrace ikoresha ikoranabuhanga ryubuzima mu gusangiza amakuru yerekeye aho umuntu ari n'ubuzima bwe n'abandi bantu ndetse n'inzego za leta, nta guhungabanya amakuru y'ibanga.
Ku ya 5 Mata 2020, TCN Coalition yose yaje kuvuka nyuma y'uko itsinda ry'abantu benshi ryifatanyije mu bikorwa nk'ibi, bigamije kugabanya ibiza, no gutuma ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo rigabanuka binyuze mu bikorwa by'ikoranabuhanga bishobora kugera ku mpera z'isi.
Ku ya 9 Mata 2020, guverinoma ya Singapore yatangaje ko yashyize ahagaragara gahunda ya BlueTrace ku baturage bose binyuze mu nyandiko yatanzwe na guverinoma yayo.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple, ibigo by'ubucuruzi bifite telefone za Android na iOS, byatangaje uburyo bushya bwo kugenzura uburibwe, bizera ko buzakingira abantu, binyuze mu gukoresha ikoranabuhanga rya Bluetooth Low Energy hamwe n'ibitabo bibika amakuru y'ibanga.
Nanone kandi, batanga urugero rw'uburyo bwo gukora ibintu.
Ku ruhande rwa Apple na Google, iyi gahunda izajya iba mu byiciro bitatu:
Gushyiraho ibikoresho bya leta bigamije kurwanya ikwirakwira rya coronavirus no kubungabunga ibimenyetso.
