Reba ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu gice gikurikira kugira ngo hatangwe umuti utanduye kandi ufasha mu kuvura COVID-19.
Ibindi bikorwa byo gushakisha bikubiyemo gutangiza urukingo na plasma ya COVID-19. SARS-CoV ifite za poroteyine 66 zishobora gukoreshwa mu kuvura, buri imwe ifite ubushobozi bwo kuvura bwinshi.
Gusuzuma ibi bice by'ingenzi by'imiterere y'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima ni ingenzi mu gukora imiti yica virusi ikora neza ku maporoteyini ya COVID-19.
Mu ma poroteyine ya SARS-CoV-2 ya kure harimo protease ya papain, RNA dependent RNA polymerase, helicase, S protein, na ADP ribophosphatase.
Hussein AA, et al. basuzumye ibipimo by'ibiyobyabwenge by'igerageza byakozwe nyuma yo gusuzuma ibipimo by'uruganda, basanga hari ibimenyetso byinshi byerekana ko umuti uhagije wo guhangana n'ikibazo cy'umuti ukomeye wica SARS-CoV-2 mu bushakashatsi bwa mbere bwo kwemeza ko ari wo ukoreshwa mu bushakashatsi bw'ibitaro.
Chloroquine ni umuti w'ibimera uhabwa abantu benshi mu gihe hari izindi ndwara.
Ku ya 18 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine bishobora kuba biri mu miti iri mu bushakashatsi bw'igeragezwa mu bitaro bya Solidarity.
