Muri Werurwe 2020, abantu ntibari bazi niba icyorezo cyanduye giha ubudahangarwa abantu bakize.
Ibipimo bisa n'ibishoboka, bitewe n'imiterere y'izindi koronavirusi, ariko abanduye COVID-19 bagomba gukurikiranwa no gusuzumwa neza.
Ubu buryo bwo kuvura bwitwa indwara y'ubwoko butandukanye, ariko ntibushobora kuvurwa n'umuntu mushya.
Iyi virusi bivugwa ko yavuye mu ishyamba, mu nyamaswa, aho indwara yari imaze igihe kirekire.
Nta muntu n'umwe wari warigeze aboneka, ariko mu kwezi k'Ukuboza 2019 icyorezo cyamaze gufata abantu benshi, cyibasira n'ibindi bihugu.
Ubushakashatsi bw'ibanze bwakozwe ku barwayi 41 basanzwemo COVID-19, bwanditswe muri Mutarama 2020 mu kinyamakuru Lancet, bwerekanye igihe ibimenyetso by'indwara byatangiriye kugaragara cyane ku wa 1 Ukuboza 2019.
Amakuru ya WHO agaragaza ko ibimenyetso byatangiye kugaragara ku itariki ya 8 Ukuboza 2019.
Hari uburyo bwinshi bwo kubara umubare w'abapfuye.
Ibipimo bihinduka bitewe n'aho umuntu ari n'igihe kandi bigira ingaruka ku bipimo, agaciro k'ubuvuzi, amahitamo y'ubuvuzi, igihe kuva umuntu atangira kugaragara no ku miterere y'abaturage nk'imyaka, uburebure n'ubuzima rusange.
Mu mpera za 2019, OMS yatanze umubare wa ICD-10 U07.1 w'urupfu ruterwa n'indwara ya SARS-CoV-2 mu bitaro na U07.1 w'urupfu ruterwa n'indwara ya COVID-19 mu bitaro cyangwa mu bitaro bitagira SARS-CoV-2.
Dukurikije amakuru ya Johns Hopkins University, umubare w'abanduye ni 6.9% (153,822/2,240,191) kuva ku ya 17 Mata 2020.
Umubare uratandukana bitewe n'akarere.Ibindi bikoresho birimo umubare w'abapfa (CFR), ugaragaza umubare w'abantu bafite uburwayi n'abapfa, n'umubare w'abapfa (IFR), ugaragaza umubare w'abantu (bafatwa kandi bazakurwaho) bapfa kubera uburwayi runaka.
Ibi byerekana igihe abantu bamwe na bamwe bamara barwaye indwara runaka.
Nubwo abantu bose badashobora guhangana n'ubwandu, kuba bahari bishobora gutanga amakuru ku mubare w'abantu banduye.
Mu gihugu cy'u Butaliyani, mu mujyi muto witwa Castiglione d'Adda, utuwe n'abantu 4.600, hapfuye abantu 80 (1.7%).
Muri Gangelt, icyorezo cyakwirakwijwe n'abari mu birori bya Carnival, cyibasira abaturage batishoboye, kandi gihitana abantu bake cyane, kandi abantu bose bapfuye bazize COVID-19 ntibaba mu itsinda ry'abapfuye.
Byongeye kandi, ubuvuzi bw'Ubudage buzakomeza gutera imbere.
Mu Buholandi, hafi 3% bashobora kuba bafite ubwandu bw'umubiri, nk'uko bigaragara mu maraso y'abatanga.
Abantu 69 (0.004% by'abatuye isi) bamaze kumenyekana ko bishwe na COVID-19.
Ubukana n'imfu by'indwara zitandukanye cyane mu bagabo n'abagore.
Ibipimo by'urupfu byari hejuru cyane ku bagabo mu bushakashatsi bwakorewe mu Bushinwa no mu Butaliyani.
Impamvu nyamukuru y'uburwayi ku bagabo ni nyuma y'imyaka 50, kandi itandukaniro hagati y'abagabo n'abagore ni nyuma y'imyaka 90.
Mu Bushinwa, umubare w'abapfa ni 2.8% by'abagabo na 1.7% by'abagabo.
Impamvu nyakuri zituma abantu batandukana ku gitsina zirazwi, ariko ibinyabuzima n'imiterere bishobora kuba ari byo bituma batandukana.
Itandukaniro ry'ubushobozi bw'umubiri hagati y'abagabo n'abagore, kugabanya ubukana n'ubukana mu bagore n'abagabo, bishobora kugaragaza ibyago byo kurwara indwara z'amaraso n'ibindi bibazo by'uburwayi mu bagore bishobora gutuma umubare w'abapfa mu bagabo wiyongera.
Mu Burayi, 57% by'abanduye ni abagabo naho 72% by'abapfuye bazize COVID-19 ni abagabo.
Muri Mata 2020, guverinoma ya Amerika yasuzumye amakuru yerekeye ubwandu bwa COVID-19.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko indwara zituruka kuri virusi nka Ebola, HIV, ibicurane na SARS zigira ingaruka ku bagabo n'abagore mu buryo butandukanye.
Abenshi mu bakora mu buvuzi, abaforomo, abagore, bafite amahirwe make yo guhura n'iyi virusi.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020 ko iyi ndwara izitwa "COVID-19".
Umuyobozi wa OMS Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus yavuze ko CO isobanura Coronavirus, VI isobanura virusi, D isobanura icyorezo, na 19 isobanura igihe cy'ibanze cy'icyorezo: 31 Ukuboza 2019.
Izina ry'inyamaswa rishobora guhitamo kuba rigizwe n'ibintu bitatu: izina ry'akarere (urugero nk'u Bushinwa), inkomoko y'inyamaswa cyangwa itsinda ry'inyamaswa.
OMS ikomeza gushyiraho amagambo "virusi ya COVID-19" na "virusi itera COVID-19" mu biganiro bya rubanda.
Iyo ndwara na virusi byombi byitwa "coronavirus".
Mu gihe icyorezo cyatangiraga mu Bushinwa, virusi na virusi byavugwaga nka "coronavirus" na "coronavirus ya Wuhan".
Muri Mutarama 2020, OMS yemeje icyorezo cy'indwara z'ubuhumekero cya 2019-nCov na 2019-nCoV nk'izina rya mbere rya virusi n'icyorezo nk'uko byagenze mu 2015 kubera ubwandu bw'ubwandu bw'indwara n'icyorezo.
Izina ry'ukuri rya COVID-19 na SARS-CoV-2 ryasohotse ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020.
Kubera ko hari uburyo buke bwo kugura ibikoresho, ababikora bakora ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi nk'ibikoresho byo guhumeka n'iby'imashini.
Mu isomo rimwe, igihe ivuriro ryo mu Butaliyani ryatumizaga ibikoresho byo guhumeka byihutirwa, umukiriya ntiyabyerekanaga mu gihe cy'isaha, undi mukiriya wo mu gace katazwi yabyerekanyeho maze atangaza 100 ku mugoroba.
Nyuma y'icyorezo cya COVID-19, amakuru, amakuru y'ibanze cyangwa amakuru y'ibanze yagiye akoreshwa cyane mu rwego rwo kwirinda, kwirinda, kuvura no kugaragaza ibimenyetso.
Abantu ni bo bashobora gukwirakwiza virusi mu zindi nyamaswa.
Ubu bushakashatsi buzaba bugamije kureba ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bwa virusi mu ngurube, ibinyamushongo n'ibindi.
Nta muti cyangwa urukingo rukora ngo iki cyorezo kiveho.
Ubushakashatsi ku isi hose ku rukingo n'umuti wa COVID-19 burimo gukorwa n'ibigo, ibigo by'ubuvuzi n'abahanga mu by'ubuvuzi.
Muri Werurwe, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangije "Icyigisho cy'Ubumwe" kigamije gusuzuma ibyago byo gukoresha imiti ine ifatanye igaragaza akamaro kanini.
Nta rukingo rw'iki cyorezo ruraboneka, ariko hari amatsinda menshi akora ku rukingo rw'ibizamini bikomeye.
Imirimo yo guhashya SARS-Cov ni ingenzi kuko SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 byombi bikoresha ACE2 mu kwinjiza mu mubiri w'umuntu.
Hari uburyo bwo gukingira bukomeje kugeragezwa.
Mbere na mbere, abashakashatsi bashakaga kuvumbura urukingo rwa virusi.
Gukoresha virusi nk'iyi, yaba ikora cyangwa ihitana, bisaba ko habaho uburyo bwo kurwanya indwara nshya ya COVID-19.
Uburyo bwa kabiri, ni uburyo bwo kuvura virusi, bugamije gukora urukingo rugabanya ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri ku zindi virusi.
Nk'uko bimeze kuri SARS-CoV-2, ubu bushakashatsi bwerekana ko poroteyine ya S-spike ifasha virusi kwinjira mu mubiri ikagira ibisubizo bya ACE2.
Uburyo bwa gatatu ni bwa virusi z'indwara z'ibicurane (DNA cyangwa RNA, uburyo bushya bwo kugaragaza virusi).
Ibizamini bya mbere by'urukingo ku buryo bumwe muri ubwo ngo bigomba gusuzumwa ku bijyanye n'umutekano n'akamaro.Ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020, icyiciro cya mbere cy'igerageza ry'urukingo cyatangiye ku bantu bane.
Uru rukingo rufite ubwoko bw'indwara ya virusi itera virusi itera SIDA. Urundi rukingo rw'umubiri rwashyizweho nk'urukingo rushobora kuvura SARS-CoV-2, ariko hari abahanga batarabyemeza.
Hariho ibizamini by'ubuvuzi birenga 300 byakozwe ku bushakashatsi kuva muri Mata 2020.
Ibizamini bitandatu na bibiri byasuzumye imiti ivura indwara mu buvuzi bw'ibimera, hamwe n'ibyigisho bine byerekeranye na hydroxychloroquine cyangwa chloroquine.
Urukingo rw'indwara z'ibyorezo ni rwo rukoreshwa cyane mu bushakashatsi mu Bushinwa, hamwe n'igeragezwa rya III rya Remdesivir mu bihugu byinshi mu mpera za Mata.
Ibizamini byo gukoresha urukingo rwa COVID-19 n'imiti bizatangira kugaragara, guhera muri Mata 2020.
Hari icyizere cy'uko hazabaho icyemezo cyo gukoresha umuti wa remdesivir, mu kwezi kwa Werurwe 2020.
Kujya mu igerageza mu bitaro byagaragaye ku barwayi bafataga imiti ya remdesivir mu buryo bwemewe.
Ibizamini byo mu rwego rwa III byakozwe muri Amerika, Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani. Chloroquine, yari isanzwe ifasha mu kuvura malariya, yasuzumwe mu Bushinwa muri Gashyantare 2020, n'ibisubizo bya mbere.
Ariko kandi, hari ibibazo by'ubushakashatsi.
Ubuyobozi bw'ubuzima bw'igihugu cya Koreya n'ubw'Ubushinwa bwemeza ko chloroquine ikoreshwa.
Ariko, ikigo cya Wuhan Institute of Virology, giteganya ko kugabanya dose y'umuti igera kuri garama imwe ku munsi, bishobora guteza akaga gakomeye kandi gashobora kwica.
Ku ya 28 Werurwe 2020, FDA yatanze amabwiriza yihutirwa yo gukoresha hydroxychloroquine na chloroquine nta ruhushya rw'abaganga mu kuvura abantu barwaye COVID-19.Inyandiko y'ibanze ya 7 ivuga ko interféron, ribavirin cyangwa umifenovir ari byo bikoreshwa mu kuvura COVID-19.
Amakuru ya mbere yerekana ko ibipimo bya ribavirin bifite akamaro ku kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 mu byumba.
Nitazoxanide irasabwa mu bushakashatsi mu mubiri nyuma y'uko ibipimo by'ibinure bya SARS-CoV-2 byagabanutse. Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko kugenzura neza poroteyine ya spike ya mbere binyuze mu murandasi wa serine 2 (TMPRSS2) ari ngombwa kuri SARS-CoV-2 binyuze mu gukorana na ACE2 receptor.
Ubushakashatsi ku chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine hamwe na azithromycin cyangwa idafite, bufite ibibazo byinshi bituma umuryango wacu w'abaganga utemera ko ikoreshwa mu bushakashatsi. Oseltamivir ntabwo itera SARS-CoV-2 mu cyumba kandi ifite uruhare runini mu kuvura COVID-19.
Ibimenyetso bya cytokine bishobora kuba ingorabahizi mu bindi byiciro bya COVID-19 bikomeye.
Hari ibimenyetso byerekana ko hydroxychloroquine ishobora kugira ubushobozi bwo kugabanya imikorere ya cytokine. Tocilizumab yashyizwe mu mabwiriza y'ubuvuzi na Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Igihugu y'Ubushinwa nyuma yo kurangiza indi nyigo nto.
Icyiciro cya 2 cy'ibizamini bidashingiye ku ivangura mu Butaliyani ntibiremewe ku bantu bafite uburwayi budahwitse.
Iyo ufashe ibipimo by'umusemburo w'amaraso kugira ngo umenye niba hari ibyago byo kutagira cytokine, bigufasha kwirinda ko ibyo bintu bibaho, bikaba bishobora no gutuma abantu bamwe na bamwe bicwa n'iyo ndwara.
Igisubizo cy'ikigo cy'ubuvuzi cya interleukin-6 cyemejwe na FDA ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu kuvura cytokine ya steroidal refractory yavuye mu miti ikoreshwa ku ngirabuzimafatizo ya CAR T, mu 2017.
Ibi, cyangwa ibimenyetso nk'ibi, byerekana ko tocilizumab ari ingenzi mu kuvura CRS.
Gutanga abasirikare b'umubiri banduye hamwe n'abanduye COVID-19 ku bantu babikeneye bigenzurwa nk'uburyo bwo kwirinda.
Ubu buryo bwakozwe mu gihe cya SARS ariko ntibutanga umusaruro.
Kwica virusi ni uburyo bwo guhangana n'iki cyorezo binyuze mu gukoresha umuti urwanya indwara ushobora gutuma umuntu agira ubudahangarwa kuri SARS-CoV-2.
Ibindi bintu, nk'ibimenyetso bya cytotoxity ya cellular na/cyangwa kurya, bishobora kuba.
Uburyo bwo kuvura abarwayi buzwi cyane, urugero nk'abarwayi bafite amaguru abiri, buragenda bugabanuka.
Gukura amaraso y'umuntu urwaye, ari yo maraso yavuye mu murwayi wafashwe n'indwara ya virusi, bishobora kwiyongera bitewe no kurwara.
